{"tid":1513103,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"825我收到張心意卡","createTime":"2019-08-28T07:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T08:10:54.000Z","uid":8751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ae2c02c9c3cabe7be1fa7a12126585b6c1e63d","tid":1513103,"uid":8751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"個日我收到一位手足張心意卡<br />\n當刻冇時間打開睇下寫乜野<br />\n番到屋企後張野都已經因爲落雨而溶溶爛爛<br />\n<br />\n個位手足大約寫左自己唔敢上前線 好對唔住etc.<br />\n因為手足唔想我將呢張心意卡既內容放上黎<br />\n但係我真係好想同你講番聲 多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線手足都要有你地呢班手足係後邊backup<br />\n我地既行動先得以成功<br />\n無論你地係和理非又好 唔敢上前線都好<br />\n只要有份上過戰場 我地就永不割席<br />\n<br />\n希望未來日子大家可以繼續加油<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"7cfda4bdc1522ba8b0d95db61eaaca56c4b59694","tid":1513103,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5CL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=9cf4b26c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5CL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=f5f4e7c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5CL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=02f40a05\" data-auto-link target=\"_bl